	dprr:hasSecondarySource <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/21> ;
	dprr:hasNotes "Nep. Att. 11.2, Plut. Brut. 35. Possibly the praetorius serving under Brutus, dismissed before Philippi for embezzlement but still stuck in the East with his son after the defeat." ;
